sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor patient as Patient
    participant nhsApp as NHS App
    participant taskingSolution as Tasking Solution
    participant ndsTestBooking as NDS Test Booking Solution
    participant nds as National Diagnostic Service (NDS)
    participant ndsDos as NDS Directory of Services (NDS Dos)

    patient ->>+ nhsApp : Access application to view tasks
    nhsApp ->>+ taskingSolution : Request list of patient tasks
    taskingSolution -->>- nhsApp : List of tasks
    nhsApp -->>- patient : Display list of tasks to patient
    patient ->>+ nhsApp: Patient selects book diagnostic test task
    nhsApp ->>+ nds: Request relevent Diagnostic Test details 
    nds -->>- nhsApp: Return Diagnostic Test Details
    nhsApp ->>- patient: Display Diagnostic Test Details to patient
    patient ->>+ ndsTestBooking: Patient confirms to book diagnostic test
    ndsTestBooking ->>+ nds: Request options for relevent test
    nds ->>+ ndsDos: Request options for selected diagnostic test (Clinic Appointments/Home Test)
    ndsDos -->>- nds: Return options for patient
    nds -->>- ndsTestBooking: Return options for patient
    ndsTestBooking -->>- patient: Display options for booking to patient    